Package: shinybreakpoint
Title: Set Breakpoint in 'Shiny'
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Grzegorz", "SmoliÅ„ski", , "g.smolinski1@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Insert 'browser()' into chosen location in reactive context
    (even when working with modules stored in separate files), what opens
    the interactive debugger and allows to inspect objects and run
    arbitrary code.
